name: TUNNEL ABSTRACT
description: for the celebration of my first 2000 followers I decided to give away 100 nfts. Thank you very much to all the artists who have supported me and connected with my art. Abstract art is a form of artistic expression that dispenses with all figuration and proposes a new reality different from the natural one. Use a visual language of shape, color, and line to create a composition that can exist independently of real-world visual references.
